'''hypothalamus''' (''plural'' '''hypothalami''')

# {{anatomy}} A region of the [[brain]] located below the [[thalamus]], forming the basal portion of the [[diencephalon]], and functioning to regulate body temperature, some metabolic processes and governing the [[autonomic nervous system]].

